<p>Progress on his Russian translation of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Alexander Kovalevsky is at Tor in Sinai, where C. G. Ehrenberg was in 1827.</p> 
<p>Has CD seen Ernst Haeckel’s new book [<hi rend="italic">Biologische Studien</hi> (1870–7)]?</p> 
